mobility.name: Mobility
mobility.description: Increases your movement speed and maximum jump height.

resilence.name: Resilience
resilence.description: Increases the amount of damage you can take before dying.

recovery.name: Recovery
recovery.description: Increases the speed at which you regain lost health.

discipline.name: Discipline
discipline.description: Discipline decreases the cooldown time of your grenades, allowing you to use them more often.

intellect.name: Intellect
intellect.description: Intellect decreases the cooldown of your Super ability, allowing you to use it more often.

strength.name: Strength
strength.description: Strength decreases the cooldown time of your melee ability, allowing you to use it more often.
